STATE of North Carolina
v.
Nicholas Nathaniel CAULEY. No. 331P01-4. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 10, 2015. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, for State of N.C. Nicholas Nathaniel Cauley, for Cauley, Nicholas Nathaniel. Frank R. Parrish, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 15th of April 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Dare County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 10th of June 2015."
